parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the 8-speed transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate or refuse to downshift, leading to difficulty stopping or accelerating, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to downshift properly
continues to push the vehicle when trying to stop
requires aggressive braking to come to a stop
hesitates or lags when accelerating
shudders or jerks when shifting gears
revs up to high RPMs
and may cause the vehicle to stall or become stuck in gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The use of soy/nut-based insulation in vehicle wiring can attract rodents and other animals, leading to damage and failure of electrical systems, which can cause a range of problems, including engine stalling, electrical fires, and loss of critical safety systems.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is typically discovered during inspection or repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle loses power or acceleration
the vehicle stalls or shuts down
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard
unusual noises or vibrations come from the transmission.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unintended acceleration of the vehicle, combined with the failure to provide adequate warning or assistive systems, can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly and unexpectedly changes lanes
accelerates without input from the driver
and fails to provide warning lights or alerts to the driver.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering module can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle hesitates or stalls
unknown warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
the vehicle becomes undrivable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The infotainment system malfunction can cause a distraction to the driver, leading to a potential accident, especially in heavy traffic conditions.
symptoms: The infotainment center reboots unexpectedly when a phone is plugged in
the radio volume suddenly becomes very loud and cannot be controlled
the driver is unable to adjust the volume
the system freezes or becomes unresponsive.
